    <abstract>
      <t>This memo specifies a prime-order group, ristretto255, suitable for safely implementing higher-level and complex cryptographic protocols. The ristretto255 group can be implemented using Curve25519, allowing existing Curve25519 implementations to be reused and extended to provide a prime-order group.</t>
